### Blog API Testing File
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or Thunder Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### 1. Register Admin User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin User",
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get All Blogs (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs

### 4. Get All Blogs with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs?status=published&category=Technology&page=1&limit=10

### 5. Search Blogs
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs?search=nodejs

### 6. Create Blog (Admin - with image)
# Note: Use Postman/Thunder Client for file upload
POST {{baseUrl}}/blogs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Form Data:
# title: My First Blog Post
# content: This is a detailed blog post...
# excerpt: A brief summary
# coverImage: [Select File]
# category: Technology
# tags: ["nodejs", "express"]
# status: published
# isFeatured: true

### 7. Get Single Blog by Slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs/my-first-blog-post

### 8. Update Blog (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/blogs/blog-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Blog Title",
  "content": "Updated content...",
  "status": "published"
}

### 9. Toggle Blog Status (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/blogs/blog-id-here/toggle-status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Like Blog
POST {{baseUrl}}/blogs/blog-id-here/like

### 11. Get Blog Stats (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/blogs/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Delete Blog (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/blogs/blog-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===== COMMENTS =====

### 13. Add Comment (Authenticated)
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blogId": "blog-id-here",
  "content": "Great article! Very informative."
}

### 14. Add Reply to Comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blogId": "blog-id-here",
  "content": "Thanks for the feedback!",
  "parentCommentId": "parent-comment-id-here"
}

### 15. Get Blog Comments
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/blog/blog-id-here?page=1&limit=20

### 16. Update Comment (Owner)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/comments/comment-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated comment text"
}

### 17. Delete Comment (Owner or Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comments/comment-id-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
